	error.

	* modules/pam_umask/pam_umask.c (search_key): Don't ignore
	EOF/error return value from fgets().

	* configure.in: Check for getline and getdelim

	* po/fi.po: Add new translations.
	* po/de.po: Likewise.
	* po/es.po: Likewise.
	* po/fr.po: Likewise.
	* po/it.po: Likewise.
	* po/ja.po: Likewise.
	* po/pt_BR.po: Likewise.
